title: Ultimate Game Trainer 1.0 by JustGame|sOnt
description:
Hey peeps!

I have decided to create and share my own Game Trainer.
I works with all the games that does not have Anti-Cheat.

The program itself is very simple.

Virustotal: https://www.virustotal.com/hu/file/e79f35ed3e128f3d27f22bcad59e8e927a12c3b011c8d3a275ae83032aa2e49b/analysis/1424506872/

Screenshot of the developing process:


The detection rate is 1/57. It DOES NOT contains virus or any other malicious code.
Use at your own risk, use if you trust.

Use of the program:

1. Run the app with Admin Rights
2. Start the game
3. Enter process name
4. Use Google or CheatEngine to get memory address
5. Enter the value (eg.: money, health etc)
6. Have fun! :-)
